  "excerpt": "<p>Get started managing and analyzing your metadata with Salesforce Entity Relationship Diagram Step by Step Guide.</p>",
  "content_html": "\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1f1f1f\">a Salesforce Entity Relationship Diagram is fastest way to orient yourself to the Salesforce data model. This visual diagram is interactive, allowing Salesforce administrators, data analysts, and other data workers understand the relational data model.</p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://app.datatoolspro.com\" title=\"Login to DataTools Pro with your Salesforce User\">Login to DataTools Pro with your Salesforce</a> User</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Select the Salesforce objects that you would like to visualize and manage.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click Entity Diagram</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Explore, Export  and share your Salesforce ERD.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Visualize your Salesforce Objects Entity Relationship Diagram</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"How to Create Salesforce Entity Relationship Diagram\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lHfOyQRie3w?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1f1f1f\">Salesforce Entity Relationship Diagrams Makes Visual Storytelling Simple</h4>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><a href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/salesforce-entity-relationship-diagrams-make-visual-storytelling-made-simple/?utm_source=linkedin&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_content=gmailzap&amp;utm_campaign=ryangpost\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/image-18.png\" alt=\"Salesforce ERD\" style=\"width:381px;height:auto\"/></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#1f1f1f\">One of the most useful tools in the admin or data professional’s toolkit are Salesforce entity relationship diagrams.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/salesforce-entity-relationship-diagrams-make-visual-storytelling-made-simple/?utm_source=linkedin&amp;utm_medium=organic&amp;utm_content=gmailzap&amp;utm_campaign=ryangpost\">Read more about visual storytelling</a></p>\n\n\n\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://scribehow.com/embed/Step-by-Step_Guide_Create_a_Salesforce_Entity_Relationship_Diagram__muiFG0yzQY2ctgFt5ah2Sg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"640\" allowfullscreen frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\n"
